Name: Thyotis Jackson
Description:
Thyotis was found face down with a cut throat and stab wounds.

 According to police, she was a "cross-dresser" working the streets. In April 2010 Ignacio Bulahan, 34, was arrested for her murder.

Name: John D. Mayo
Description:
John's body was sawn apart and their remains spread out over a seven mile area. The head has not yet been found.

Note that we do not know the exact date of John's death, only that it occurred during May 2004.
